'''005  Ask the user to enter three numbers. Add together the first two numbers and then multiply 
this total by the third. Display the answer as The answer is [answer].'''
Number1=int(input('Kindly Share your first number'))
number2=int(input('Kinldy share your second number'))
number3=int(input('Kindly share your third number'))
Answer=(Number1+number2)*number3

print('The answer is',Answer)
